  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="head">
        <%=  render :partial => "/common/practice_menu" %>
      </div>

      <div class="main">
        <div class="zh_test_left">
          <div class="zh_test_top"></div>
          <div class="zh_test_middle">
            <%= yield  %>
          </div>
          <div class="zh_test_bottom"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="zh_test_right">
          <div class="zhTest_r_title">说明</div>
          <div class="zhTest_r_con">
            <div>综合训练共有五个任务，完成一个任务自动进入下一任务，五个任务完成时，即完成一篇完整的综合训练。</div>
            <dl>
              <dt>Task I</dt>
              <dd>听一边录音，做下面全部小题。</dd>
              <dt>Task II</dt>
              <dd>听一边录音，理解意思，可以和答案对照看自己是否理解有偏差。</dd>
              <dt>Task III</dt>
              <dd>根据短文意思，拖动相应的单词，放到短文的空白处。</dd>
              <dt>Task IV</dt>
              <dd>根据各段短文意思，拖动相应的单词，放到各段短文的空白处。</dd>
              <dt>Task V</dt>
              <dd>听各段录音，填写各段录音的内容。</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="clear"></div>
      <div class="foot">
        <%=  render :partial => "/common/footer" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% if !is_vip? && @practies_count >= Constant::PRACTICES_COUNT %>
      <div class="zhezhao" style="display: block; height: 100%;position:fixed; "></div>
      <div class="service_tishi" style="top: 238.5px; left: 481.5px; display: block; ">
        <div class="se_ts_x"><a href="/user/homes/<%= Category::TYPE_IDS[:english_fourth_level] %>">X</a></div>
        <div class="se_ts_text">普通用户只能享受5篇综合训练内容的免费试用，升级VIP用户您将获得全部60篇的训练内容，现在就升级吧!</div>
        <div class="open_vip_btn"><button onclick="window.location.href='/users/get_vip'"></button></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <%=  render :partial => "/common/flash_div" %>
  </body>
